data.description: NOW OFFERING UP TO $5,000 towards Buyer's Concessions with an accepted offer!  New virtually staged photos show you all this home has to offer!  Welcome to 109 Windsor Dr. in beautiful Daphne, Alabama! This charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is located in Lake Forest off of the highway 98 entrance with NO HOA.  Downstairs you will find not one, but TWO separate living spaces, three bedrooms (one en-suite) and one guest bathroom. Upstairs you will find a spacious bedroom, bathroom and office space/5th bedroom. Enjoy all of the GREAT storage space this home has to offer whether it’s closet storage, window bench storage, or attic access.  Relax with a cup of coffee or entertain friends and family on the large covered side patio. The backyard has mature trees providing shade and privacy, a storage shed with a greenhouse, and a LARGE workshop connected to the carport and equipped with power. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and entertainment, this home is the perfect place to call your own.  *Information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer or buyer's agent to verify all information.  Features: New laminate 3/2021, Roof – 3/2021, HVAC- 2015ish, Water heater – 2018. Breaker Boxes have been updated with electrical
